The pool/jacuzzi setting is great considering you are in a busy downtown area.	I didn't go into the pool but the pool area had a great view, there were lots of chairs and a fire in case it was cold.	The pool was a hit with the kids, as was the brownie sundae by the pool!!	The work out facility is really one of the better hotel fitness rooms I have used with the treadmills facing large windows with pool and water views.	The infinity pool is a great way to spend an afternoon, and the staff was very attentive.